<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(فَمَتَى فِي الدَّهْر نلقى ... شَيخنَا بدر الأهله)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
